OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 20 APR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1964FBBC TV is renamed BBC One,
OL,7,Ffollowing the launch of BBC Two.
OL,8,
OL,9,FThe channel's on-screen identity is
OL,10,Fupdated with the introduction of a new
OL,11,Fglobe symbol (the second globe device).
OL,12,
OL,13,CG2009FBBC Parliament's on-screen
OL,14,Fpresentation is updated to bring it
OL,15,Finto line with the core BBC TV News
OL,16,Fbranding, first seen a year earlier.
OL,17,
OL,18,FBoth packages were produced by
OL,19,FLambie-Nairn.
OL,20,
OL,21,
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
